msgid ""
"To activate the *Leads* setting, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and check the box labeled, :guilabel:`Leads`. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Para activar la funciﺣﺏn de *leads*, vaya a :menuselection:`CRM --> "
"Configuraciﺣﺏn --> Ajustes`, seleccione la casilla con el "
"nombre :guilabel:`Leads` y luego haga clic en :guilabel:`Guardar`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:None
msgid "Leads setting on CRM configuration page."
msgstr ""
"Captura de pantalla de la opciﺣﺏn de leads en la pﺣ۰gina de configuraciﺣﺏn de "
"CRM."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:20
msgid ""
"Activating this feature adds the :guilabel:`Leads` menu option to the header "
"bar located along the top of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Activar esta funciﺣﺏn agrega la opciﺣﺏn de menﺣﭦ :guilabel:`Leads` a la barra "
"ubicada en la parte superior de la pantalla."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:None
msgid "Leads menu on CRM application."
msgstr "Menﺣﭦ de leads en la aplicaciﺣﺏn CRM."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:26
msgid ""
"Once the *Leads* setting has been activated, it applies to all sales teams "
"by default. To turn off leads for a specific team, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Sales Teams`. Then, select "
"a team from the list to open that team's configuration page. Clear "
"the :guilabel:`Leads` checkbox, located beneath the :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"field, then click :icon: `fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que habilitaste la funciﺣﺏn de *leads*, esta se aplica de forma "
"predeterminada a todos los equipos de ventas. Para desactivar los leads en "
"un equipo especﺣ­fico, ve a :menuselection:`CRM --> Configuraciﺣﺏn --> Equipos "
"de ventas`, selecciona un equipo de la lista para abrir su pﺣ۰gina de "
"configuraciﺣﺏn, desmarca la casilla :guilabel:`Leads` ubicada abajo del "
"campo :guilabel:`Equipo de ventas` y luego haz clic en :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`Guardar`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:36
msgid "Convert a lead into an opportunity"
msgstr "Convertir un lead en una oportunidad"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:38
msgid ""
"To convert a lead into an *opportunity*, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app "
"--> Leads`, and click on a lead from the list to open it."
msgstr ""
"Para convertir un lead en una *oportunidad*, vaya a :menuselection:`CRM --> "
"Leads` y haga clic en un lead de la lista para abrirlo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:42
msgid ""
"Attempting to convert a lead with a 100% probability into an opportunity "
"will result in an error message."
msgstr ""
"Querer convertir un lead con una probabilidad del 100% en una oportunidad "
"resultarﺣ۰ en un mensaje de error."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:0
msgid ""
"The error message that appears when attempting to convert a 100% probability "
"lead into\n"
"an opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Captura de pantalla del mensaje de error que aparece al intentar convertir "
"un lead con probabilidad del 100% en\n"
"una oportunidad."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:49
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Convert to Opportunity` button, located at the top-left "
"of the page."
msgstr ""
"Haga clic en el botﺣﺏn :guilabel:`Convertir a oportunidad` ubicado en la "
"parte superior izquierda de la pﺣ۰gina."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:None
msgid "Create opportunity button on a lead record."
msgstr ""
"Captura de pantalla donde se muestra el botﺣﺏn para convertir una oportunidad "
"en un registro de lead."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:54
msgid ""
"This opens a *Convert to opportunity* pop-up. Here, select "
"the :guilabel:`Convert to opportunity` option in the :guilabel:`Conversion "
"Action` field."
msgstr ""
"Esto abrirﺣ۰ una ventana emergente *Convertir a oportunidad*. Aquﺣ­, en el "
"campo :guilabel:`Acciones de conversiﺣﺏn`, selecciona la "
"opciﺣﺏn :guilabel:`Convertir a oportunidad`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:57
msgid ""
"Then, select a :guilabel:`Salesperson` and a :guilabel:`Sales Team` to which "
"the opportunity should be assigned. Neither field is required, but if a "
"selection is made in the :guilabel:`Salesperson` field, the :guilabel:`Sales "
"Team` is automatically populated based on the assignee's assigned team."
msgstr ""
"Despuﺣ۸s, selecciona un :guilabel:`vendedor` y un :guilabel:`equipo de "
"ventas` a los que se les debe asignar la oportunidad. Ninguno de los campos "
"es obligatorio, aunque si seleccionas a un :guilabel:`vendedor`, el "
"campo :guilabel:`Equipo de ventas` se llenarﺣ۰ en automﺣ۰tico segﺣﭦn el equipo "
"al que pertenezca el vendedor."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:61
msgid ""
"If the lead has already been assigned to a salesperson or a team, these "
"fields automatically populate with that information."
msgstr ""
"Estos campos se completarﺣ۰n de forma automﺣ۰tica con la informaciﺣﺏn "
"correspondiente si el lead ya estaba asignado a un vendedor o a un equipo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:64
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Customer` heading, choose from the following options:"
msgstr ""
"En la secciﺣﺏn :guilabel:`Cliente` seleccione una de las opciones a "
"continuaciﺣﺏn:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Create a new customer`: Choose this option to use the information "
"in the lead to create a new customer record."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Crear un nuevo cliente`: Elige esta opciﺣﺏn para usar la "
"informaciﺣﺏn del lead para crear un nuevo registro de cliente."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Link to an existing customer`: Choose this option, then select a "
"customer from the drop-down menu to link this opportunity to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vincular a un cliente existente`: Para vincular esta oportunidad "
"al registro de un cliente existente, elige esta opciﺣﺏn y luego selecciona un "
"cliente del menﺣﭦ desplegable."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:71
msgid ""
"Lastly, when all configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Create "
"Opportunity`."
msgstr ""
"Por ﺣﭦltimo, cuando haya completado todas las configuraciones, haga clic "
"en :guilabel:`Crear oportunidad`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:None
msgid "Create opportunity pop-up."
msgstr ""
"Captura de pantalla de la ventana emergente para crear una oportunidad."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:76
msgid ""
"To view the newly created opportunity, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --"
"> My Pipeline`."
msgstr ""
"Vaya a :menuselection:`CRM --> Mi flujo` para ver la oportunidad que acaba "
"de crear."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:79
#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/pipeline/merge_similar.rst:35
msgid "Merging similar leads and opportunities"
msgstr "Fusionar leads y oportunidades similares"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:81
msgid ""
"If a :guilabel:`Similar Leads` smart button appears at the top of the page "
"for the lead, a similar lead or opportunity already exists in the database. "
"Before converting the current lead, click the smart button to check if the "
"leads should be merged."
msgstr ""
"Si aparece un botﺣﺏn inteligente de :guilabel:`Leads similares` en la parte "
"superior de la pﺣ۰gina del lead, ya existe un lead o una oportunidad similar "
"en la base de datos. Antes de convertir este lead, haz clic en el botﺣﺏn "
"inteligente para investigar si lo mejor serﺣ­a fusionar los leads."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:0
msgid "Close up of a lead with emphasis on the Similar Leads smart button."
msgstr ""
"Captura de pantalla de un lead con el botﺣﺏn inteligente Leads similares "
"resaltado."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:88
msgid ""
"To merge this lead with an existing similar lead or opportunity, click "
"the :guilabel:`Convert to Opportunity` button and select :guilabel:`Merge "
"with existing opportunities` in the :guilabel:`Conversion Action` field. "
"This generates a list of the similar leads/opportunities to be merged."
msgstr ""
"Para fusionar este lead con un lead u oportunidad existente similar, haz "
"clic en :guilabel:`Convertir en oportunidad`, selecciona la "
"opciﺣﺏn :guilabel:`Fusionar con oportunidades existentes` en el "
"campo :guilabel:`Acciones de conversiﺣﺏn`. Esto generarﺣ۰ una lista de leads u "
"oportunidades similares que se pueden fusionar."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:93
msgid ""
"When merging, Odoo gives priority to whichever lead/opportunity was created "
"in the system first, merging the information into the first created lead/"
"opportunity. The resulting record is an opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Al realizar la fusiﺣﺏn, Odoo prioriza el lead u oportunidad que se creﺣﺏ "
"primero en el sistema y fusionarﺣ۰ la informaciﺣﺏn en ese lead oportunidad. La "
"fusiﺣﺏn de estos registros resultarﺣ۰ en una oportunidad."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:3
msgid "Create leads (from email or manually)"
msgstr "Crear leads (desde un correo o de forma manual)"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:8
msgid ""
"Leads can be added to the *CRM* app from custom email aliases, and by "
"manually creating new records. This is in addition to the leads and "
"opportunities created in the app through the :doc:`website contact form "
"<opportunities_form>`."
msgstr ""
"Ademﺣ۰s de los leads y oportunidades que el sistema crea en la aplicaciﺣﺏn "
"*CRM* a travﺣ۸s del :doc:`formulario de contacto del sitio web "
"<opportunities_form>`, tambiﺣ۸n puedes agregar leads con un alias de correo o "
"crear los registros de forma manual."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:12
msgid ""
"First, ensure the *Leads* feature is enabled in the database by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Tick "
"the :guilabel:`Leads` checkbox, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Primero vaya a :menuselection:`CRM --> Configuraciﺣﺏn --> Ajustes` y "
"asegﺣﭦrese de que la funciﺣﺏn *Leads* estﺣ۸ habilitada. Seleccione la "
"casilla :guilabel:`Leads` y haga clic en :guilabel:`Guardar`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:19
msgid "Configure email aliases"
msgstr "Configurar los alias de correo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:21
msgid ""
"Each sales team has the option to create and utilize their own unique email "
"alias. When messages are sent to this address, a lead (or opportunity), is "
"created with the information from the message."
msgstr ""
"Los equipos de ventas pueden crear y utilizar su propio alias de correo. Una "
"vez que reciban mensajes en esta direcciﺣﺏn de correo, el sistema crearﺣ۰ un "
"lead (o una oportunidad) con toda la informaciﺣﺏn correspondiente."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:25
msgid ""
"To create or update a sales teams' email alias, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Sales Teams`. Click on a "
"team from the list to open the team's details page."
msgstr ""
"Ve a :menuselection:`CRM --> Configuraciﺣﺏn --> Equipos de ventas` para crear "
"o actualizar los alias de correo de un equipo de ventas. Haz clic en uno de "
"los equipos de la lista para abrir su respectiva pﺣ۰gina de detalles."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:None
msgid "The sales team details page, focused on the email alias section."
msgstr ""
"Captura de pantalla de la pﺣ۰gina de detalles del equipo de ventas, destaca "
"la secciﺣﺏn de alias de correo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:32
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Email Alias` field, enter a name for the email alias, or "
"edit the existing name. In the :guilabel:`Accept Emails From` field, use the "
"drop-down menu to choose who is allowed to send messages to this email alias:"
msgstr ""
"Escribe el nombre del alias de correo en el campo :guilabel:`Alias de "
"correo` o edita el existente. Usa el menﺣﭦ desplegable del "
"campo :guilabel:`Aceptar correos electrﺣﺏnicos de` para elegir quiﺣ۸nes pueden "
"enviar mensajes a este alias de correo:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:36
msgid ":guilabel:`Everyone`: messages are accepted from any email address."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Todos`: Para aceptar mensajes de cualquier direcciﺣﺏn de correo "
"electrﺣﺏnico."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Authenticated Partners`: only accepts messages from email "
"addresses associated with a a partner (contact or customer) record."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Contactos autenticados`: Para solo aceptar mensajes de "
"direcciones de correo electrﺣﺏnico asociadas a un registro de contacto o "
"cliente."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Followers only`: only accepts messages from those who are "
"following a record related to the team, such as a lead or opportunity. "
"Messages are also accepted from team members."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Solo seguidores`: Para solo aceptar mensajes de personas que son "
"seguidores de un registro relacionado al equipo, como un lead o una "
"oportunidad. Tambiﺣ۸n se aceptarﺣ۰n mensajes de miembros del equipo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Authenticated Employees`: only accepts messages from email "
"addresses that are connected to a record in the *Employees* app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Empleados autenticados`: Para solo aceptar mensajes de "
"direcciones de correo que estﺣ۸n vinculadas a algﺣﭦn registro de la aplicaciﺣﺏn "
"*Empleados*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:45
msgid "Leads created from email"
msgstr "Leads creados desde un correo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:47
msgid ""
"Leads created from email alias messages can be viewed by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Leads`. Click a lead from the list to open "
"it, and view the details."
msgstr ""
"Los leads creados a travﺣ۸s de los mensajes recibidos por el alias de correo "
"estﺣ۰n disponibles en :menuselection:`CRM --> Leads`. Haz clic en uno de los "
"leads de la lista para abrirlo y ver sus detalles."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:50
msgid ""
"The email received by the alias is added to the *chatter* thread for the "
