#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:3
msgid "CRM activities and activity plans"
msgstr "Actividades y planes de actividades en CRM"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:5
msgid ""
"Within the *CRM* app, *activities* are follow-up tasks tied to *leads* and "
"*opportunities* that are visible in the chatter. A set of preconfigured "
"activity types is available in the *CRM* app, but custom activity types may "
"also be created to suit business needs. To view the list of available "
"activity types in the *CRM* app, open the app and navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Activity Types`. This page shows both "
"Odoo-created activities and any custom activities."
msgstr ""
"Dentro de la aplicaciﺣﺏn *CRM*, las *actividades* son tareas de seguimiento "
"vinculadas a *leads* y *oportunidades* que aparecen en el chatter. La "
"aplicaciﺣﺏn *CRM* incluye algunos tipos de actividades preconfigurados, pero "
"tambiﺣ۸n puedes crear tipos personalizados segﺣﭦn las necesidades que tenga tu "
"empresa. Para ver la lista de tipos de actividades disponibles en *CRM*, "
"abre la aplicaciﺣﺏn y ve a :menuselection:`Configuraciﺣﺏn --> Tipos de "
"actividad`. Esta pﺣ۰gina muestra las actividades creadas por Odoo y las "
"actividades personalizadas."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:12
msgid ""
"Different applications support different activity types. To see the complete "
"list of activity types, go to the :menuselection:`Settings app`, then scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Discuss` section, and click the :guilabel:`Activity Types` "
"link."
msgstr ""
"Cada aplicaciﺣﺏn admite distintos tipos de actividades. Para ver la lista "
"completa, ve a :menuselection:`Ajustes`, dirﺣ­gete a la "
"secciﺣﺏn :guilabel:`Conversaciones` y haz clic en :guilabel:`Tipos de "
"actividad`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:17
msgid "Default and custom activity types"
msgstr "Tipos de actividad predeterminados y personalizados"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:19
msgid "The preconfigured activity types for the *CRM* app are:"
msgstr ""
"Los tipos de actividad preconfigurados en la aplicaciﺣﺏn *CRM* son los "
"siguientes:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:21
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Email`: Adds a reminder to the chatter prompting the salesperson "
"to send an email."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Correo electrﺣﺏnico`: Agrega un recordatorio al chatter para que "
"el vendedor envﺣ­e un correo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:22
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Call`: Opens a calendar link where the salesperson can schedule a "
"phone call."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Llamada`: Abre un enlace al calendario para que el vendedor "
"programe una llamada telefﺣﺏnica."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:23
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Meeting`: Opens a calendar link where the salesperson can "
"schedule a meeting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Reuniﺣﺏn`: Abre un enlace de calendario donde el vendedor puede "
"programar una reuniﺣﺏn."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:24
msgid ":guilabel:`To Do`: Adds a general reminder task to the chatter."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Por hacer`: Agrega una tarea de recordatorio general al chatter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:25
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Upload Document`: Adds a link on the activity where an external "
"document can be uploaded. Note that the *Documents* app is **not** required "
"to utilize this activity type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Subir documento`: Agrega un enlace en la actividad donde puedes "
"subir un documento externo. Ten en cuenta que **no** necesitas la aplicaciﺣﺏn "
"*Documentos* para usar este tipo de actividad."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/utilize_activities.rst:29
msgid ""
"If other Odoo applications are installed, such as *Sales* or *Accounting*, "
"additional activity types may appear in the *CRM* app's *Activity Types* "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Si instalas otras aplicaciones de Odoo, como *Ventas* o *Contabilidad*, es "
"posible que aparezcan otros tipos de actividad en la pﺣ۰gina *Tipos de "
"actividad* de la aplicaciﺣﺏn *CRM*."

