"discount nomenclature (e.g., a barcode starting with `2250`), Odoo "
"automatically applies the defined price reduction of 50% to the milk during "
"the current transaction."
msgstr ""
"Una caja de leche caduca maﺣﺎana. Al escanear un cﺣﺏdigo de barras que sigue "
"la nomenclatura de descuentos (por ejemplo, uno que empieza con `2250`), "
"Odoo aplica una reducciﺣﺏn de precio del 50% de forma automﺣ۰tica a la leche "
"en la transacciﺣﺏn actual."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:132
msgid "Barcode nomenclature"
msgstr "Nomenclatura de los cﺣﺏdigos de barras"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:134
msgid ""
"Barcode nomenclatures explain how barcodes are identified and classified. "
"When a barcode is scanned, it is linked to the first rule that matches its "
"pattern. This pattern syntax adheres to a standardized method of prefix "
"matching; a barcode is considered a match if its prefix aligns with the "
"pattern."
msgstr ""
"La nomenclatura de los cﺣﺏdigos de barras explica cﺣﺏmo se identifican y "
"clasifican los cﺣﺏdigos. Al escanear un cﺣﺏdigo de barras, el sistema lo "
"vincula con la primera regla que coincide con su patrﺣﺏn. Esta sintaxis sigue "
"un mﺣ۸todo estandarizado de coincidencia por prefijo, asﺣ­ que un cﺣﺏdigo se "
"considera vﺣ۰lido si su prefijo coincide con el patrﺣﺏn."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:139
msgid ""
"Patterns also define how numerical values ﻗsuch as weight, price, or "
"percentageﻗ are encoded into the barcode. These are indicated by `{NNN}`, "
"where the `N`'s define the position of the digits."
msgstr ""
"Los patrones tambiﺣ۸n definen cﺣﺏmo se codifican los valores numﺣ۸ricos como "
"peso, precio o porcentaje en el cﺣﺏdigo de barras. Se indican con `{NNN}`, "
"donde las `N` definen la posiciﺣﺏn de los dﺣ­gitos."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:142
msgid ""
"To view or edit these rules, go to the :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/"
"settings>`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Inventory` section, and click "
"the :icon:`oi-arrow-right` (:guilabel:`Internal Link`) icon next "
"to :guilabel:`Barcode Nomenclature`."
msgstr ""
"Para ver o editar estas reglas, ve a los :ref:`ajustes del PdV <pos/use/"
"settings>`, dirﺣ­gete a la secciﺣﺏn :guilabel:`Inventario` y haz clic en el "
"icono :icon:`oi-arrow-right` (:guilabel:`Enlace interno`) ubicado junto "
"a :guilabel:`Nomenclatura del cﺣﺏdigo de barras`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:146
msgid ""
"For discount tags, use the :guilabel:`Discount Barcodes` rule. The default "
"pattern is :guilabel:`22{NN}`, meaning the barcode must start with `22`, "
"followed by two digits representing the discount percentage."
msgstr ""
"Usa la regla :guilabel:`Cﺣﺏdigos de barras de descuentos` con las etiquetas "
"de descuento. El patrﺣﺏn predeterminado es :guilabel:`22{NN}`, lo que indica "
"que el cﺣﺏdigo debe empezar con `22`, seguido de dos dﺣ­gitos que representan "
"el porcentaje de descuento."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:None
msgid "discount tags nomenclature setting form"
msgstr ""
"Captura de pantalla del formulario de configuraciﺣﺏn de la nomenclatura de "
