"para acceder con facilidad (por ejemplo, `Amazon.se`). Los "
"campos :guilabel:`identificador API`, :guilabel:`regiﺣﺏn` y :guilabel:`URL de "
"Seller Central` deben contener respectivamente los valores de *Marketplace "
"ID*, la regiﺣﺏn de Amazon seleccionada y la *URL de Seller Central* de la "
"documentaciﺣﺏn de Amazon."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/amazon_connector/setup.rst:144
msgid ""
"Once the marketplace is saved, update the Amazon Account configuration by "
"going to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings --> "
"Connectors --> Amazon Sync --> Amazon Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Una vez hecho esto, actualice la configuraciﺣﺏn de la cuenta de Amazon "
"en :menuselection:`Ventas --> Configuraciﺣﺏn --> Ajustes --> Conectores --> "
"Sincronizaciﺣﺏn de Amazon --> Cuentas de Amazon`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/amazon_connector/setup.rst:147
msgid ""
"Select the account on which to use the new marketplace, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Marketplaces` tab, and click on :guilabel:`Update available "
