"pﺣ۰gina :guilabel:`Aplicaciones`, busque el bloque de la "
"aplicaciﺣﺏn :guilabel:`Gastos` y haga clic en :guilabel:`activar`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:178
msgid ""
"The page automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, "
"where the :guilabel:`Expenses` app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"La pﺣ۰gina se actualizarﺣ۰ de formar automﺣ۰tica y volverﺣ۰ al tablero principal "
