#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:125
msgid "Import relation fields, attributes, and variants"
msgstr "Importar campos de relaciﺣﺏn, atributos y variantes"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:127
msgid ""
"It's important to note that an Odoo object is always related to many other "
"objects. For example, a product is linked to product categories, attributes, "
"vendors, and related information. These links/connections are known as "
"relations."
msgstr ""
"Es importante tener en cuenta que un objeto de Odoo siempre se relaciona con "
"muchos otros objetos. Por ejemplo, un producto estﺣ۰ vinculado con categorﺣ­as "
"de productos, atributos, proveedores y otra informaciﺣﺏn relacionada. Estos "
"vﺣ­nculos se conocen como relaciones."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:132
msgid ""
"To import product relations, the records of the related object **must** be "
"imported *first* from their own list menu."
msgstr ""
"Para importar relaciones de productos, *primero* **debes** importar los "
"registros del objeto relacionado desde su propio menﺣﭦ de lista."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:136
msgid "Relation fields"
msgstr "Campos de relaciﺣﺏn"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:138
msgid ""
"In Odoo, product forms include several fields that can be modified and "
"customized at any time. These fields are available on every tab of a product "
"form. While these fields can be edited directly on the product form, they "
"can also be modified via a product import."
msgstr ""
"En Odoo, los formularios de productos incluyen varios campos que puedes "
"modificar y personalizar en cualquier momento. Estos campos estﺣ۰n "
"disponibles en todas las pestaﺣﺎas del formulario del producto. Aunque puedes "
"editar estos campos desde el formulario del producto, tambiﺣ۸n puedes "
"modificarlos al importar los productos."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:142
msgid ""
"As mentioned, relation fields of this nature can **only** be imported for "
"products if they already exist in the database. For example, if a user "
"attempts to import a product with a *Product Type*, it must be one of the "
"preconfigured product types in the database (e.g., *Tracked Product*, "
"*Untracked*, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Como mencionamos anteriormente, los campos de relaciﺣﺏn de este tipo **solo** "
"pueden importarse a los productos si ya existen en la base de datos. Por "
"ejemplo, si un usuario intenta importar un producto con un *tipo de "
"producto*, este debe existir en la base de datos (por ejemplo *Producto con "
"seguimiento*, *Sin seguimiento*, entre otros)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:147
msgid ""
"To import information for a relation field on a product import template "
"spreadsheet, add the name of the field as a column name/title on the "
"spreadsheet. Then, on the appropriate product line, add the desired relation "
"field option."
msgstr ""
"Para importar informaciﺣﺏn a un campo de relaciﺣﺏn en una hoja de cﺣ۰lculo de "
"plantilla de importaciﺣﺏn de productos, debe agregar el nombre del campo como "
"un tﺣ­tulo o nombre de columna en la hoja de cﺣ۰lculo. Despuﺣ۸s, agregue la "
"opciﺣﺏn del campo de relaciﺣﺏn en la lﺣ­nea de producto correspondiente."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:151
msgid ""
"When all desired relation field information has been entered, save the "
